summary: An email from an Assistant United States Attorney in the Southern District of New York transmitting interview notes as an attachment. The document itself is a brief cover email, with the substantive content presumably contained in the attached PDF file.

events.title: Transmission of Interview Notes
events.description: An Assistant United States Attorney sends an email with the subject 'Today's notes' and an attachment titled '2021-02-11, interview notes.pdf'.

keyFacts: The document is an email dated February 11, 2021, from a federal prosecutor.
The email's purpose is to transmit an attachment labeled 'interview notes.pdf'.
The substantive investigative information is contained in the attached PDF, which is not part of the provided text.
